    <exercisegroup>
        <title>Technology</title>
        <introduction>
          <p>For the following exercises, solve the equations algebraically, and then use a calculator to find the values on the interval <m>[0,2π).</m> Round to four decimal places.</p>
        </introduction>
        <exercise xml:id="PRECALC-rTHU5lxH7P-parts" original="PRECALC/modules/m49398/index.cnxml" license="CC-BY-4.0">
